Introduced Version
HOUSE BILL No. 1354
_____
DIGEST OF INTRODUCED BILL
Citations Affected: IC 5-10-8.
Synopsis: Employee health plans for county elected officials. Requires
a county to offer a program of group insurance to each county elected
official if the county offers the program of group insurance to county
employees and at least one county elected official.
Effective: July 1, 2026.
May
January 8, 2026, read first time and referred to Committee on Local Government.
2026 IN 1354—LS 6109/DI 154

